==English==

===Noun===
'''[[happy]] [[birthday]]'''

# Said or written to a person who is celebrating his or her [[birthday]] in order to convey the good [[wish]]es of the speaker or writer.
#: '''''Happy Birthday''', Joe! Have a fantastic [[party]]!''

====Synonyms====
*[[many happy returns]]
*[[many happy returns of the day]]

